{"article_id":"sCo5G5T2HuLM7PId","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New York and New Jersey will automatically quarantine all medical workers","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"returning from Ebola-hit West African countries ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"and the U.S. government is considering the same step","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"after a doctor","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"who treated patients in Guinea","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"came back infected ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"officials said on Friday .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The steps","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"announced by the two states ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"which go beyond the current restrictions","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"being imposed by the U.S. government on travelers from Liberia , Sierra Leone or Guinea ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"came as medical detectives tried to retrace the steps of the infected physician , Dr. Craig Spencer .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"`` Increasing the screening process is necessary .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"it reduces the risk to New Yorkers and the residents of New Jersey , ''","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"said New York Governor Andrew Cuomo .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Cuomo ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"who appeared with the governor of neighboring New Jersey , Chris Christie , at a news conference ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"had earlier in the day sought to reassure New Yorkers","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that Ebola 's threat was limited the day","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"after Spencer tested positive for the virus .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"In Washington , President Barack Obama also sought to reassure a worried public with an Oval Office hug of Dallas nurse Nina Pham ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"who was declared Ebola-free on Friday","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"after catching the virus from a Liberian patient","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"who died .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"But Republican lawmakers ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"many of whom for weeks have called for a tougher response to Ebola ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"continued their criticism of the administration at a congressional hearing .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"In the first instance of the new move by the two governors , a female healthcare worker","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"who had treated patients in West Africa","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and arrived at the Newark , New Jersey , airport","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"was ordered into quarantine .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"Cuomo said","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"the U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"( CDC )","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"had agreed","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that individual states have the right","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to exceed federal requirements .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"A federal quarantine of healthcare workers","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"returning to the United States from the three West African countries","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"was one of a number of options","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"being discussed by administration officials ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Tom Skinner , a CDC spokesman , told Reuters .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Dr. Spencer , 33 ,","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"who spent a month with the humanitarian group Doctors Without Borders in Guinea ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"was the fourth person","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"diagnosed with the virus in the United States","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"and the first in its largest city .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Dr. Mary Travis Bassett , New York 's health commissioner , said","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"Spencer was awake","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"and talking to family and friends by cellphone","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"and was listed in stable condition in Bellevue Hospital 's isolation unit .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"The Obama administration has implemented a series of steps","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"aimed at preventing the further spread of Ebola in the United States","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"but has stopped short of a travel ban on people from Liberia , Sierra Leone or Guinea","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"called for by some politicians .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"The United States is funneling travelers from those countries through five airports","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"conducting special screening for signs of infection","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"and is requiring them to report to health authorities for the 21-day Ebola virus incubation period .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"The airports include a New York City airport and a New Jersey airport","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"that serve the metropolitan area .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"`` We want to strike the right balance","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"of doing what is best","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"to protect the public 's health","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"while not impeding whatsoever our ability","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"to combat the epidemic in West Africa .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Our risk here will not be zero","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"until we stop the epidemic there , ''","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Skinner said .","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"Pham , one of two nurses from a Dallas hospital","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"infected with Ebola","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"after treating the first patient","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"diagnosed with the disease in the United States ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"walked out smiling and unassisted from the Bethesda , Maryland , hospital","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"where she was treated .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Emory University Hospital in Atlanta and the CDC also confirmed","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"that the other nurse , Amber Vinson , no longer had detectable levels of virus","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"but did not set a date","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"for her to leave that facility .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Pham ,","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"who was transferred to the U.S. National Institutes of Health","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"( NIH )","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Clinical Center in Bethesda , Maryland , from the Dallas hospital on Oct. 16 , thanked her doctors at a news briefing .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Looking fit in a dark blazer and a turquoise blouse ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Pham said","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"even though she no longer is infected ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"`` I know","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"that it may be a while before I have my strength back . ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"she looked forward to seeing her family and her dog .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Photos of the Oval Office meeting showed Obama","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"hugging Pham .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"Reporters and television cameras were not allowed in for the meeting .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"Dr. Anthony Fauci , director of the NIH 's National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases , said","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"he could not pinpoint any one factor","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"that contributed to Pham 's speedy recovery .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"it could be any of a number of factors ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"including the fact","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that `` she 's young and very healthy ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"and was able to get intensive care very quickly .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Spencer finished his work in Guinea on Oct. 12","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"and arrived at John F. Kennedy International Airport in New York on Oct. 17 .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Six days later , he was quarantined at Bellevue Hospital with Ebola .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"The three previous cases","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"diagnosed in the United States","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"were in Dallas .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Three people","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"who had close contact with Spencer","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"were quarantined for observation .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"The doctor 's fiancée was among them","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"and was isolated at the same hospital ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"and all three were still healthy ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"officials said .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"New York City Mayor Bill de Blasio said","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"city health department detectives were retracing all the steps","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"taken by Spencer ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"but said","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"the doctor poses no threat to others","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"and urged New Yorkers to stick to their daily routines .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Health officials emphasized","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"that the virus is not airborne","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"but is spread through direct contact with bodily fluids from an infected person","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"who is showing symptoms .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Republican Representative Darrell Issa of California ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"who chairs the House of Representatives Oversight Committee ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"blasted the `` bumbling '' administration response ,","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"it had been characterized by missteps and ill-considered procedures","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"to protect U.S. healthcare workers at home and troops in West Africa .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Local officials told New Yorkers","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"they were safe","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"even though Spencer had ridden subways ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"taken a cab","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and visited a bowling alley in Brooklyn between his return from Guinea and the onset of symptoms .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Authorities on Friday declared the bowling alley safe .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"Cuomo said","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"that unlike in Dallas , New York officials had time","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"to thoroughly prepare and drill for the possibility of a case","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"emerging in the city .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"`` From a public health point of view , I feel confident","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"that we 're doing everything","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"that we should be doing ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"and we have the situation under control , ''","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Cuomo said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":291,"left":197,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":188,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":173,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":157,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":152,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":151,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":147,"right":150,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":2,"right":149,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":160,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":159,"right":15,"relatio